You attempt to interrupt a creature in the process of casting a spell. If the creature is casting a spell of "rare" tier or lower, their spell fails and has no effect.

!! Legendary-Tier

When you cast //{{!!title}}// as a legendary-[[tier|spell tier]] spell, you may counter other legendary-tier spells.